txt.en: Complete: Shadows of Caras Tilion Slayer (Advanced)
You have become known as an exceptional hunter among the peoples of Felegoth and Dale.
Many more wicked Easterlings have fallen before you. The Kingdom of Dale is grateful for your aid.
The Taurogrim menace has been culled. The Elves of Felegoth are grateful for your aid.
Defeat many enemies of the Free Peoples in Eryn Lasgalen and the Dale-lands.
Caras Tilion has been purged of much of the lingering evil of Dol Guldur. The Elves of Felegoth are grateful for your aid.
Many more wandering Orcs have been defeated. Felegoth and Dale are grateful for your aid.
Defeat many enemies of the Free Peoples in Eryn Lasgalen and the Dale-lands.
